WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Hello! Today I’ll walk you through the Ingoo merchant profile.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
Right at the top, you see your available balance for withdrawal.

00:09.000 --> 00:16.000
The first option is "Withdraw". Tap to pick the amount you want to withdraw

00:16.000 --> 00:22.000
and click "Send request". Note: the send-request option

00:22.000 --> 00:29.000
is only available between the 15th and the 17th. Back on the main screen, we have "History".

00:29.000 --> 00:38.000
Here you can track your withdrawals: all, awaiting review, awaiting payment, paid

00:38.000 --> 00:45.000
and, if something goes wrong, "Failed". Below that, the "My Merchants" option.

00:45.000 --> 00:51.000
Here you can review every venue of yours that has an Ingoo station.

00:51.000 --> 00:55.000
Tap a venue to see its details:

00:55.000 --> 01:02.000
name, contact, category, opening days and address.

01:02.000 --> 01:07.000
Below that, you see the revenue percentage.

01:07.000 --> 01:12.000
And underneath, the stations available at that venue.

01:14.000 --> 01:19.000
You also get the team info: sales managers and operations managers.

01:19.000 --> 01:24.000
Tap the phone icon to get in touch and request

01:24.000 --> 01:30.000
a technical visit. Back on the main menu, we have "My Devices".

01:30.000 --> 01:37.000
Here you see all your devices available on your network.

01:37.000 --> 01:43.000
Under "Available" you check whether the station is online; if it’s turned off

01:43.000 --> 01:49.000
or off-network, it shows as offline. If that happens, go back to the home menu

01:49.000 --> 01:56.000
and tap "My Feedback". In "Feedback Issues" pick your venue,

01:56.000 --> 02:02.000
choose a platform staff member, describe the problem, and below

02:02.000 --> 02:08.000
upload an image. Back on the home menu, we have "Order Revenue",

02:08.000 --> 02:12.000
where you can review every order placed at your stations.

02:12.000 --> 02:18.000
Under "Settings" you can change the language and reset your password.

02:18.000 --> 02:27.000
Any questions, go to www.ingoobrasil.com.br and tap your city’s support.
